### Frontend — Page 4: AI Configuration (`/config`)

#### [NEW] [page.tsx](file:///c:/work/pre_sale/DS_service/object_detect/factory_safety/safety-app/app/config/page.tsx)
**AI Configuration Panel** showcasing MLOps flexibility:

**Section 1 — Detection Toggles**:
- Toggle switches (ShadCN `Switch`) for each detection class:
  - `[x] Hard Hat / Helmet`
  - `[x] Safety Vest`
  - `[ ] Face Mask`
  - `[ ] Safety Goggles`
  - `[ ] Gloves`
- Each toggle shows an icon and description

**Section 2 — Confidence Threshold**:
- `Slider` component (0–100%) with real-time value display
- Visual guide: "Low → More detections, more false positives" ↔ "High → Fewer detections, higher precision"

**Section 3 — Zone Configuration** (bonus):
- Map/grid of monitored zones with enable/disable toggles
- Zone names editable inline

**Save button** → sends config as parameters to backend on next detection API call.

