### Backend — Schemas

#### [NEW] [common.py](file:///c:/work/pre_sale/DS_service/object_detect/factory_safety/backend/schemas/common.py)
Generic `APIResponse[T]` model (copied from Lead Scoring).

#### [NEW] [detection.py](file:///c:/work/pre_sale/DS_service/object_detect/factory_safety/backend/schemas/detection.py)
```python
class BoundingBox(BaseModel):
    x: float      # top-left x (0-1 normalized)
    y: float      # top-left y
    width: float
    height: float

class Detection(BaseModel):
    label: str            # "helmet", "vest", "no_helmet"
    confidence: float     # 0.0 – 1.0
    bbox: BoundingBox
    is_violation: bool

class DetectionResult(BaseModel):
    detections: list[Detection]
    image_url: str | None
    processed_at: datetime
    total_persons: int
    violations_count: int
    compliance_rate: float
```

#### [NEW] [incident.py](file:///c:/work/pre_sale/DS_service/object_detect/factory_safety/backend/schemas/incident.py)
Incident log entry schema.

